concept_set_name: [VSAC Bulk-Import test] Cirrhosis or other liver disease
concept_set_version_title: [VSAC Bulk-Import test] Cirrhosis or other liver disease (v1)
comments: Exported from VSAC and bulk imported to N3C.
intention: Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes that identify patients with a diagnosis of cirrhosis or other liver disease.; Data Element Scope: This value set is developed for the diagnosis QDM datatype. It can potentially be used for other datatypes as well.; Inclusion Criteria: Include all diagnosis codes associated with cirrhosis or other liver disease.
limitations: Exclusion Criteria: Exlcude diagnosis codes for neonatal and juvenile liver diseases.
provenance: Steward: The Joint Commission; OID: 2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1029.63; Code System(s): SNOMEDCT,ICD9CM,ICD10CM; Definition Type: Grouping; Definition Version: Latest; Accessed: 2022-01-20 15:54:47

comments: Exported from VSAC and bulk imported to N3C.
intention: Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent post operative hemorrhaging.; Data Element Scope: This value set may use Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to the finding category or diagnosis code. limitations: Exclusion Criteria: Concepts that do not indicate a post operative hemorrhage.
